<item>
            <title>[LU-9665] LNET not shutting down properly</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9665</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When ever a reboot/shutdown command is issued from OS&lt;br/&gt;
It&apos;s failing because LNET didn&apos;t shutdown properly&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>CentOS 7.2</environment>
